'''萊安·克里斯蒂'''（{{lang-en|Ryan Christie}}；{{bd|1995年|2月22日}}）是一位[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是[[中場|中場]]。現效力於[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|般尼茅夫]]，[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭足球代表隊]]成員。

==生平==
萊安的父親查理·克里斯蒂也是一位職業球員。他出身自[[因弗內斯足球俱樂部|因弗內斯]]的青訓系統<ref name="Ryan Christie sign his first professional contract">{{cite news|title=Christie's son among new youth signings|url=http://www.inverness-courier.co.uk/Sport/Football/Christies-son-among-new-youth-signings-13052011.htm|publisher=Inverness Courier|date=15 May 2011|accessdate=18 May 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009124200/http://www.inverness-courier.co.uk/Sport/Football/Christies-son-among-new-youth-signings-13052011.htm|archive-date=2014-10-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他在2015年轉會凱爾特人<ref>{{cite news|title=Ryan Christie: Celtic agree four-year deal for Inverness player|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34106143|publisher=BBC News|date=1 September 2015|accessdate=1 September 2015|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224150812/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34106143|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也曾是蘇格蘭國青隊的一員<ref>{{cite news|title=Christie scores call-up to Scotland under-21s|url=http://www.highland-news.co.uk/Sport/Football/Inverness-Caley-Thistle/Christie-scores-call-up-to-Scotland-under-21s-25082014.htm|publisher=Highland News|date=25 August 2014|accessdate=23 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111338/http://www.highland-news.co.uk/Sport/Football/Inverness-Caley-Thistle/Christie-scores-call-up-to-Scotland-under-21s-25082014.htm|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

